<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>IOZERA — Philippines AI Industrial Park</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
:root{
  --black:#08090C;
  --white:#F4F2EE;
  --blue:#1570EF;
  --blue2:rgba(21,112,239,0.12);
  --blue3:rgba(21,112,239,0.25);
  --gold:#C9A55A;
  --gold2:rgba(201,165,90,0.15);
  --steel:#10151E;
  --steel2:#161D2A;
  --muted:#4B5A6E;
  --muted2:rgba(244,242,238,0.55);
  --border:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  --green:#22C55E;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{background:var(--black);color:var(--white);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:300;overflow-x:hidden;}

/* NAV */
nav{
  position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:999;
  display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
  padding:16px 48px;
  background:rgba(8,9,12,0.92);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
}
.nav-logo img{height:28px;filter:brightness(0) invert(1);}
.nav-pills{display:flex;gap:6px;}
.nav-pill{
  width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--muted);
  cursor:pointer;transition:all .3s;border:none;
}
.nav-pill.active{background:var(--blue);transform:scale(1.3);}
.nav-conf{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;
  text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);border:1px solid rgba(201,165,90,0.3);
  padding:5px 12px;
}

/* SLIDES */
.slide{
  min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;
  padding:100px 48px 60px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.inner{max-width:1160px;margin:0 auto;width:100%;}

/* UTILS */
.label{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;
  text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--blue);margin-bottom:18px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
}
.label::before{content:'';width:24px;height:1px;background:var(--blue);}
.label.gold{color:var(--gold);}
.label.gold::before{background:var(--gold);}

.h1{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(56px,8vw,108px);line-height:.92;letter-spacing:1px;}
.h2{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,64px);line-height:.97;letter-spacing:.5px;}
.h3{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,36px);line-height:1;letter-spacing:.5px;}
.body{font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--muted2);}
.body-sm{font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--muted2);}
.blue{color:var(--blue);}
.gold{color:var(--gold);}
.green{color:var(--green);}
.divider{width:100%;height:1px;background:var(--border);margin:32px 0;}

/* GRID HELPERS */
.g2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:64px;align-items:center;}
.g3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:2px;}
.g4{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:2px;}

/* CARDS */
.card{background:var(--steel);padding:28px 22px;transition:all .2s;cursor:default;}
.card:hover{background:var(--steel2);transform:translateY(-3px);}
.card-blue{border-top:2px solid var(--blue);}
.card-gold{border-top:2px solid var(--gold);}
.card-green{border-top:2px solid var(--green);}

/* CALLOUT */
.callout{padding:20px 22px;border-left:2px solid var(--blue);background:var(--blue2);margin-top:20px;}
.callout.gold{border-left-color:var(--gold);background:var(--gold2);}
.callout-label{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--blue);margin-bottom:6px;}
.callout.gold .callout-label{color:var(--gold);}

/* SPEC TABLE */
.spec-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;padding:11px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);gap:16px;}
.spec-k{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);}
.spec-v{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--white);text-align:right;}
.spec-v.b{color:var(--blue);}
.spec-v.g{color:var(--gold);}

/* STATUS PILLS */
.pill{
  display:inline-block;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:8px;
  letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:3px 8px;border:1px solid;
}
.pill-op{color:var(--green);border-color:rgba(34,197,94,.3);background:rgba(34,197,94,.07);}
.pill-blue{color:var(--blue);border-color:var(--blue3);background:var(--blue2);}
.pill-muted{color:var(--muted);border-color:var(--border);}
.pill-gold{color:var(--gold);border-color:rgba(201,165,90,.3);background:var(--gold2);}

/* FADE ANIM */
.fu{opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px);transition:opacity .65s ease,transform .65s ease;}
.fu.vis{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
.fu.d1{transition-delay:.1s;}.fu.d2{transition-delay:.2s;}.fu.d3{transition-delay:.3s;}.fu.d4{transition-delay:.4s;}.fu.d5{transition-delay:.5s;}

/* SCROLL HINT */
.scroll-hint{
  position:absolute;bottom:28px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:6px;
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;
  text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);
}
.scroll-line{width:1px;height:32px;background:linear-gradient(var(--muted),transparent);animation:sp 2s ease-in-out infinite;}
@keyframes sp{0%,100%{opacity:.3}50%{opacity:1}}

/* ═══════════════════════════════
   SLIDE 1 — COVER
═══════════════════════════════ */
#s1{background:var(--black);}
.cover-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr;gap:72px;align-items:center;}
.cover-eyebrow{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;
  text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:20px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
}
.cover-eyebrow::before{content:'';width:20px;height:1px;background:var(--gold);}
.cover-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(58px,8.5vw,112px);line-height:.9;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:24px;}
.cover-sub{font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--muted2);max-width:440px;margin-bottom:36px;}
.cover-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);border:1px solid var(--border);}
.cs{padding:20px 16px;border-right:1px solid var(--border);position:relative;}
.cs:last-child{border-right:none;}
.cs::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:var(--blue);}
.cs-val{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:36px;color:var(--blue);line-height:1;margin-bottom:3px;}
.cs-lbl{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);}
.cover-tags{display:flex;gap:0;margin-top:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.ctag{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);padding:8px 16px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-right:none;}
.ctag:last-child{border-right:1px solid var(--border);}

.cover-visual{
  background:var(--steel);border:1px solid var(--border);
  aspect-ratio:1;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.cv-grid{
  position:absolute;inset:0;
  background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(21,112,239,.05) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(21,112,239,.05) 1px,transparent 1px);
  background-size:36px 36px;
}
.cv-glow{
  position:absolute;width:280px;height:280px;border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(21,112,239,.2) 0%,transparent 70%);
  top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
}
.cv-center{position:relative;z-index:2;text-align:center;}
.cv-num{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:88px;color:var(--blue);line-height:1;}
.cv-sub{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:4px;}
.cv-corner-tl,.cv-corner-br{position:absolute;width:28px;height:28px;}
.cv-corner-tl{top:14px;left:14px;border-top:2px solid var(--gold);border-left:2px solid var(--gold);}
.cv-corner-br{bottom:14px;right:14px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--gold);border-right:2px solid var(--gold);}
.cv-badge{
  position:absolute;bottom:14px;left:14px;
  background:rgba(8,9,12,.92);border:1px solid var(--blue3);
  padding:6px 12px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:8px;
  letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--blue);
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════
   SLIDE 2 — TEAM
═══════════════════════════════ */
#s2{background:var(--steel);}
.team-img-wrap{
  width:100%;border:1px solid var(--border);overflow:hidden;
  margin-top:28px;
}
.team-img-wrap img{width:100%;display:block;}
.partners-bar{
  margin-top:20px;padding:18px 24px;
  border:1px solid var(--border);background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:32px;flex-wrap:wrap;
}
.partners-bar-label{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;
  text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);flex-shrink:0;
}
.partners-bar-names{
  display:flex;gap:24px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;
}
.pname{font-size:12px;color:rgba(244,242,238,.4);letter-spacing:.5px;font-weight:500;}

/* ═══════════════════════════════
   SLIDE 3 — TIMOTHY NGO
═══════════════════════════════ */
#s3{background:var(--black);}
.ceo-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:.9fr 1.1fr;gap:72px;align-items:center;}
.ceo-visual{
  background:var(--steel);border:1px solid var(--border);
  aspect-ratio:.85;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:center;
}
.ceo-bg{
  position:absolute;inset:0;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d1520,#12203a,#0a1830);
}
.ceo-glow{
  position:absolute;width:240px;height:240px;border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(21,112,239,.25) 0%,transparent 70%);
  top:30%;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
}
.ceo-initials{
  position:relative;z-index:2;font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;
  font-size:96px;color:var(--blue);opacity:.15;line-height:1;padding-bottom:40px;
}
.ceo-nameplate{
  position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;
  background:rgba(8,9,12,.9);border-top:2px solid var(--blue);
  padding:16px 20px;
}
.ceo-name{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:28px;letter-spacing:1px;}
.ceo-role{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--blue);margin-top:2px;}

.ceo-content{}
.ceo-quote{
  font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,36px);
  line-height:1.05;color:var(--white);margin:20px 0 28px;
  padding-left:20px;border-left:3px solid var(--blue);
}
.ceo-pills{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;margin-top:20px;}
.ceo-pill{
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;padding:13px 16px;
  background:var(--steel);border-left:2px solid transparent;
  transition:all .2s;cursor:default;
}
.ceo-pill:hover{border-left-color:var(--blue);background:var(--steel2);}
.ceo-pill-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blue);flex-shrink:0;}
.ceo-pill-text{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--muted2);}
.ceo-companies{
  display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:24px;
}
.ceo-co{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1.5px;
  text-transform:uppercase;padding:6px 12px;
  border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--muted);
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════
   SLIDE 4 — ABOUT IOZERA
═══════════════════════════════ */
#s4{background:var(--steel);}
.about-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:64px;align-items:start;}
.stack-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;margin-top:24px;}
.stack-row{
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:44px 1fr;
  background:var(--steel2);transition:all .2s;cursor:default;
  border-left:3px solid transparent;
}
.stack-row:hover{border-left-color:var(--blue);}
.stack-num{
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:20px;color:var(--blue);
  opacity:.3;border-right:1px solid var(--border);
}
.stack-content{padding:18px 16px;}
.stack-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:.5px;color:var(--blue);margin-bottom:4px;}
.stack-body{font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(244,242,238,.55);}

.diff-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2px;margin-top:24px;}
.diff-card{background:var(--black);padding:20px 16px;border-top:2px solid var(--border);transition:all .2s;cursor:default;}
.diff-card:hover{border-top-color:var(--blue);}
.diff-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:.5px;color:var(--white);margin-bottom:6px;}
.diff-body{font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(244,242,238,.5);}

/* ═══════════════════════════════
   SLIDE 5 — THESIS
═══════════════════════════════ */
#s5{background:var(--black);}
.thesis-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:72px;align-items:start;}
.thesis-quote{
  font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,40px);
  line-height:1.05;padding:20px 0 20px 20px;border-left:3px solid var(--blue);
  margin:24px 0;
}
.cons-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;margin-top:16px;}
.cons-item{
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:13px 16px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.025);border-left:2px solid transparent;
  transition:all .2s;font-size:13.5px;color:var(--muted2);cursor:default;
}
.cons-item:hover{background:var(--blue2);border-left-color:var(--blue);}
.ci{font-size:14px;width:20px;text-align:center;flex-shrink:0;}

.adv-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2px;margin-top:16px;}
.adv-card{
  background:var(--blue2);border:1px solid var(--blue3);
  padding:20px 16px;transition:all .2s;cursor:default;
}
.adv-card:hover{background:rgba(21,112,239,.2);}
.adv-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:var(--blue);margin-bottom:6px;}
.adv-body{font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(244,242,238,.6);}

/* ═══════════════════════════════
   SLIDE 6 — MARKET CAPABILITY
═══════════════════════════════ */
#s6{background:var(--steel);}
.cap-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:64px;align-items:start;}
.cap-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-top:24px;font-size:13px;}
.cap-table th{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;
  text-transform:uppercase;padding:10px 14px;text-align:left;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--muted);
}
.cap-table th.hl{color:var(--blue);background:var(--blue2);}
.cap-table td{padding:13px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.03);color:var(--muted2);vertical-align:top;line-height:1.5;}
.cap-table td.hl{color:var(--white);background:rgba(21,112,239,.04);font-weight:500;}
.cap-table tr:hover td{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);}
.cap-table tr:hover td.hl{background:var(--blue2);}
.ck{color:var(--blue);font-weight:700;}
.cx{color:rgba(244,242,238,.2);}

.insight-box{
  margin-top:20px;padding:20px 22px;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(21,112,239,.08),rgba(21,112,239,.04));
  border:1px solid var(--blue3);
}
.ib-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:18px;color:var(--blue);margin-bottom:8px;}
.ib-body{font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--muted2);}

/* ═══════════════════════════════
   SLIDE 7 — GLOBAL PIPELINE
═══════════════════════════════ */
#s7{background:var(--black);}
.pipe-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:64px;align-items:start;}
table.pipe{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-top:24px;font-size:13px;}
table.pipe th{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:10px 12px;text-align:left;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--muted);}
table.pipe td{padding:12px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.03);color:var(--muted2);}
table.pipe tr.ph td{color:var(--white);background:var(--blue2);}
table.pipe tr.op td{color:var(--green);}
table.pipe tr:hover td{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);}
table.pipe tr.ph:hover td{background:rgba(21,112,239,.1);}

.pipe-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2px;margin-top:24px;}
.ps{background:var(--steel);padding:20px 16px;}
.ps-val{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:34px;color:var(--blue);line-height:1;margin-bottom:3px;}
.ps-lbl{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);}

.roark-card{
  margin-top:20px;padding:20px 22px;
  border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,.25);background:rgba(34,197,94,.05);
}
.rc-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:18px;color:var(--green);margin-bottom:6px;}
.rc-body{font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--muted2);}

/* ═══════════════════════════════
   SLIDE 8 — WHY PHILIPPINES
═══════════════════════════════ */
#s8{background:var(--steel);}
.compare-wrap{overflow-x:auto;margin-top:28px;}
table.cmp{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;}
table.cmp th{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:12px 16px;text-align:left;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--muted);}
table.cmp th.ph{color:var(--blue);background:var(--blue2);}
table.cmp td{padding:13px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.03);color:var(--muted2);line-height:1.5;vertical-align:top;}
table.cmp td.ph{color:var(--white);background:rgba(21,112,239,.04);font-weight:400;}
table.cmp td.dim{color:rgba(244,242,238,.25);}
table.cmp tr:hover td{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);}
table.cmp tr:hover td.ph{background:var(--blue2);}
.cmp-note{
  margin-top:20px;padding:16px 20px;border:1px solid var(--border);
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;
  color:var(--muted2);font-style:italic;
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════
   SLIDE 9 — THE LAND
═══════════════════════════════ */
#s9{background:var(--black);}
.land-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr;gap:64px;align-items:start;}
.land-img-box{
  position:relative;border:1px solid var(--border);overflow:hidden;
}
.land-img-box img{width:100%;display:block;}
.land-img-overlay{
  position:absolute;inset:0;
  background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(8,9,12,.7) 0%,transparent 50%);
}
.land-img-badge{
  position:absolute;bottom:14px;left:14px;
  background:rgba(8,9,12,.92);border:1px solid var(--blue3);
  padding:6px 12px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:8px;
  letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--blue);
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════
   SLIDE 10 — DATA VALUE
═══════════════════════════════ */
#s10{background:var(--steel);}
.value-hero{
  text-align:center;padding:48px 32px;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(21,112,239,.06),rgba(21,112,239,.02));
  border:1px solid var(--blue3);margin-top:28px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.vh-v{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:120px;color:var(--blue);opacity:.06;position:absolute;top:-10px;right:24px;line-height:1;}
.vh-label{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--blue);margin-bottom:12px;}
.vh-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,54px);line-height:1;margin-bottom:16px;}
.vh-body{font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--muted2);max-width:700px;margin:0 auto 28px;}

.value-bars{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:48px;align-items:center;margin-top:40px;}
.vb-side{}

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<script>
(function(){
  const slides = document.querySelectorAll('.slide');
  const pills = document.getElementById('pills');

  slides.forEach((_,i)=>{
    const p = document.createElement('button');
    p.className='nav-pill';
    p.setAttribute('aria-label','Slide '+(i+1));
    p.onclick=()=>slides[i].scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'});
    pills.appendChild(p);
  });

  const fuEls = document.querySelectorAll('.fu');
  const obs = new IntersectionObserver(entries=>{
    entries.forEach(e=>{
      if(e.isIntersecting){
        if(e.target.classList.contains('slide')){
          const idx=Array.from(slides).indexOf(e.target);
          document.querySelectorAll('.nav-pill').forEach((p,i)=>p.classList.toggle('active',i===idx));
        }
        if(e.target.classList.contains('fu')) e.target.classList.add('vis');
      }
    });
  },{threshold:0.12});

  slides.forEach(s=>obs.observe(s));
  fuEls.forEach(el=>obs.observe(el));
})();
</script>
</body>
</html>
